data.description: Two-story open concept home at an affordable price. Located in the Entrada development in historic St. Augustine, FL. Take advantage of this opportunity and move right into this spacious open floor plan on a Cul de sac lot. Five bedrooms and three full baths with a great master suite. Natural gas community with tankless hot water, smart home features, and keyless entry. Amenity center, with pool, fitness center, splash pad, playground and dog park. Entrada is zoned for top-rated St. Johns County Schools and is minutes away from highways, shopping, outlet malls, and dining. Warranties on property (HVAC, appliances, structure, etc.) convey to new owner. Why wait to build when this property is already completed and waiting for its new owners to move in. Don't miss out on this opportunity.
